    "Let x ≃ s y iff x ⊑ s y and y ⊑ s x.",
    "◁If ⟨S, ⊑⟩ is such that every state is refined by a minimal point (see Definition 4.14), then x ⊑ s y iff every minimal point that refines x also refines y.",
